snippet.title: AQUAMAN 2 (2022) !!! Teaser Trailer - Jason Momoa, Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Aquaman has been blinded in a mysterious event. Years have passed and soon he regains his sight. However, damage to his land has been done. Its up to him and Mera to find out what happened.
